{"tid":110475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲打擊炒樓　強令華人海外買家售房產","createTime":"2017-02-06T16:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T14:31:08.000Z","uid":34286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fa527e493598ca9cf50412c505672f7a5ddec9","tid":110475,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"澳洲打擊炒樓　強令華人海外買家售房產<br />\n<br />\n澳洲近年吹起炒樓熱潮，甚至有外國人到當地炒樓，令當地樓價大升，首次置業買家難以入市。為了打擊炒樓活動，澳洲政府日前強制15名外國人脫售非法收購的房產，當中包括來自中國、印度、印度、伊朗、馬來西亞、英國以及德國的海外投資者。<br />\n<br />\n英媒報道，澳洲政府正在加強管制海外投資者。自去年5月以來，澳洲政府已經強制外國人脫售61個非法收購的房地產，涉額逾1.7億澳元。另外，海外投資者收購房地產前，必須先向政府申請許可。非澳洲籍人士只能購買一手房地產，不得收購二手物業。<br />\n<br />\n據國際地產研究中心「Demographia」調查顯示，自2009年至今，澳州悉尼樓價已上漲逾一倍，令悉尼成為全球第二房價難以負擔的城市，僅次於香港。澳洲政府已透過增加印花稅等方法，遏止海外人士在澳洲炒樓的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170206/photo/bknint-20170206163307641-0206_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170206193230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170206%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170206163307641-0206_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170206193230&h=40726404&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d069684c7ee6c85dc2efdc6aa2017ff6c1cf930","tid":110475,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:48:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c708ad3225089051f23e387fea31a96fff4ce40d","tid":110475,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf97a1db4f1abfd6e3461aea5d1bb780b974e30a","tid":110475,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T14:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}